# Express API

Canonical structure: [server/sub.md](mdc:server/sub.md).

- Flow: `routes` → `controllers` → `models`
- Use `middlewares/validate.js` on mutating routes
- DB changes only in `models/`; keep router and controller contracts stable
- Export `app` from `app.js`; tests import app without listening

NEVER put SQL/DB or business rules directly in route files.
